title: Call of duty Modern warfare 3 full game
description:
This is the complete game.....
It's not the blackbox version,nothing is ripped....
Multiplayer is not missing....
Final size = 15.5gb approximately.......

* Just run setup.exe in disc 1 folder(It will take 5-10 minutes to extract)

* It will start rebuilding the data automatically.
* Please be patient. It normally takes about 2 hours....

Launch the game from the desktop using run as administrator.....
